subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: Upsets in the women’s bracket at Wimbledon showcased the game’s depth and parity as Nicole Vaidisova toppled defending champion Amelie Mauresmo and Marion Bartoli ousted Jelena Jankovic.
